Hello all, here is an everquest question. I have a
46th level ranger and soon I will be hitting 50th
level and my alternet advancement ( I hope I got the
spelling right) will kick in, I'm not sure how to
handle the points when I have the ability to add them,
I wanted too know if there is a site I can go to that
will let me know which ones I should use for a ranger.

Luis
